ate final, which is good. I need to consider the guideline against using reflection directly; maybe that’s not applicable here. Importing `IOException` seems necessary only for the catch block. I could improve the implementation by avoiding the custom `URLStreamHandler` if the `ResourceBundle` control can use `getResourceAsStream` instead. The public API doesn't accommodate Control either, which might be an issue. However, we may need to focus on targeting the test source root correctly. It seems I need to finalize my thoughts succinctly.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_001072dd249c3c05016a1196a1499081a0a9b11c5cdbb16faf\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqEZbEMBnsVWlz-cX3kG1vPWL-44bKpinK3tysU9ePQAM4m43p38dV1GykZxdL9hKFAsIExg_tGJj3UtyF-dhFsuvrvRbGdD_ZLu6Qf8pLMfNplXOgpSETNhUP7i1OSxE1x4Mo5FgkiMMofTksuqlk998JfGn9o6-o64ePCN8eKva8a1LuJiYBON_GF7yKlzMdHycRmlDjA2MjjB3c_Ilub-TzDQizLZ8SYNmKLsO7waMROyAEO-IvjQoB4LibGs-qXJF7vX4QtTeQsKEyEHYw-0nRqQ5qPu_576EGDRN7FRWWir0nWUiE1LxKNmVgPC1sv8hSAny4UNxabBweqaftUco9-nAWd02bhNxCdBbuBR0CwKdI3Vd3bUM3LMZ42T0Mho_-qmh_fwyP5wWhU_h2ZolLFEQN0NDfLVMX4wrUufVQTng1UpovSM5DKx6sRCPzjm8vhxYbXG--wIT_GShsM8KSK4NfQEj12Pt9_nHW8Bg6884dpAM3UR3eK2-DXVNrHHQCXEclx5F4kR78Qs9TIB77NqFIrudCdWBaLCgqLtx19i2OVBBXp8WZgcAvioi7Jb9PEe-wiRiHYPWOi7dzch6sd0h0EIbl2v1NJLGMMAJmVjgzyk1SQmT9CQgqeYSqbedAlWXHK90AM94O8Dzy1xllmCNTP8e1tC-HfnHzhhWOa5zI-r1f-9BQhUHF1IUKw03lKi7mwW_3Kx1PcpXKzgF9M7XZZTMH83Mc5_WwW8ea5wSLG4jBJNLnE1zKlfnI63ZtMXddcYAhRrQeqpptkraX_xO0WUPTkh3dZwlwEmsIG82c1vPPRHuxYtE9ra9IeZ5cLibVoXCtyq8oNyET9dqzVhB7e5Oaz0ZcfGFS5sgE_hP6kV4wxM-GFicjRVoeUurkWdgPG6p9-Ijyl1KDsgvsKBh_ooAOfQ3grAWb9d1yr1Pq-zfqnV_Oy6Mf7HVK9rMrAV0B-aTD5P70tlUSq-duLmRHT9IWU9sQoXTGaIm680o9C39Lag5XhPjbnnxK_KbUz54DNGQrlShqp1rlcWjyLXyX9zMvwQRVZ8Vn8-Vxa8ZUmkejFB4aJ4gKu6D40zvBe7_GBERAlGPIkbFWxuXaDvKOV1HC5eW015cY3Yflu0VrU_lWFwRaxry6P3QgMXPiiBH0n7sXVMGE1LAY_e8K_toBQkzZGxsFPgGdJh-C83DX4dZKpKEapmahRMEga9-mtr0Ym_epi6Ri_0UGIWXq6ktSzRdNl9YZv_6PB5uK2UL4rlTyInPRCCFKzNVvJwaRAKFPH4IWq4XcQQfYKDLy9BHGSR