ed lines. Since this library class is reported as `Unknown Source` with no line number, the test can execute the call site but the current coverage reporter cannot mark it covered.\n\nSo this appears to be an instrumentation/reporting limitation for this HSQLDB 2.4.1 class rather than a remaining behavioral test gap.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_001072dd249c3c05016a1196c4013481a0a112b725c3d3a4ba\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1429, "output": 2277, "cacheRead": 66048, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 69754, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1779537567495, "responseId": "resp_001072dd249c3c05016a1196a06d4481a0b30bbec186060403"}}
